WEBVTT

01:39.479 --> 01:43.520
[Road to Success]

01:44.700 --> 01:47.910
[Episode 12]

01:56.200 --> 01:57.560
Ms. Lin, you're awake?

01:57.560 --> 01:58.640
Did you sleep well?

02:00.120 --> 02:01.150
I fell asleep?

02:01.790 --> 02:02.800
Where are they?

02:02.950 --> 02:04.410
They went to buy some food.

02:06.070 --> 02:07.680
You guys have already finished cleaning?

02:07.680 --> 02:08.560
Almost.

02:09.240 --> 02:10.310
Ms. Lin,

02:10.910 --> 02:12.150
aren't you curious

02:12.150 --> 02:13.680
how you

02:13.680 --> 02:14.630
ended up here?

02:15.710 --> 02:16.430
Right.

02:16.430 --> 02:17.829
Wasn't I sleeping there?

02:18.030 --> 02:20.400
That's because Coach made us do it.

02:23.750 --> 02:24.520
Be careful.

02:34.360 --> 02:35.560
Keep your voice down.

03:00.960 --> 03:02.400
Coach even reminded us

03:02.400 --> 03:03.710
to be quiet,

03:03.710 --> 03:05.040
afraid of waking you up.

03:09.360 --> 03:10.120
Ms. Lin,

03:10.120 --> 03:11.430
you're blushing.

03:12.750 --> 03:13.590
Am I?

03:14.800 --> 03:16.070
It must be the heat.

03:16.070 --> 03:19.400
You're underestimating me
if you think I'd blush over this.

03:20.910 --> 03:22.910
-The laziest teacher in the world
-They're back.

03:22.910 --> 03:24.470
has finally woken up.

03:24.470 --> 03:25.310
I'm sorry.

03:25.310 --> 03:26.120
I got up too early this morning

03:26.120 --> 03:27.579
and couldn't help you out.

03:27.800 --> 03:30.079
-Boss.
-It's fine. We're here, so don't worry.

03:30.079 --> 03:31.430
You went to buy food?

03:31.430 --> 03:32.190
How about this?

03:32.190 --> 03:33.430
To thank you,

03:33.430 --> 03:35.630
I'll arrange the projector myself.

03:35.630 --> 03:37.560
You put in the effort, and I'll pay.

03:38.079 --> 03:39.470
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

03:39.470 --> 03:40.800
Spicy beef rice.

03:40.800 --> 03:42.400
I added a steamed egg for you.

03:42.630 --> 03:43.360
Is there...

03:43.360 --> 03:44.840
Yes, extra spicy,

03:44.840 --> 03:45.750
no cilantro.

03:45.750 --> 03:46.840
-I'll take one.
-Give me one.

03:46.840 --> 03:47.440
Go away.

03:47.470 --> 03:49.280
-Eat whatever you get.
-You're not allowed to pick.

03:49.280 --> 03:49.840
These are all...

03:49.840 --> 03:50.800
Thank you.

03:50.800 --> 03:52.400
I'm so touched.

03:52.400 --> 03:54.050
Why is there
one pair of chopsticks missing?

03:54.050 --> 03:55.050
[Receive Money by QR Code]

03:54.430 --> 03:55.360
The last one gets no chopsticks.

03:55.360 --> 03:56.360
Take his quickly!

03:56.400 --> 03:57.360
Wait. The chopsticks are here.

03:57.360 --> 03:58.150
I don't have my phone with me.

03:58.150 --> 03:59.079
Your beef is mine now.

03:59.079 --> 03:59.870
Then pay me next time.

03:59.870 --> 04:03.150
-Lin Lu, how dare you!
-The QR Code is still him.

04:03.150 --> 04:04.030
Sorry.

04:04.030 --> 04:04.960
Excuse me.

04:04.960 --> 04:06.230
Ms. Lin, Mr. Wang,

04:06.360 --> 04:08.030
I brought your photos.

04:08.030 --> 04:10.030
These are photos of the older Lins.

04:10.030 --> 04:11.120
-I printed an extra set.
-Thank you.

04:11.120 --> 04:11.680
Thank you, sir.

04:11.680 --> 04:12.430
No problem.

04:12.430 --> 04:13.800
And these are your couple photos.

04:13.800 --> 04:15.680
I printed an extra set of those too.

04:15.680 --> 04:17.269
What... What photos?

04:22.920 --> 04:23.680
Here.

04:23.680 --> 04:24.480
When I was a kid,

04:24.480 --> 04:25.870
I attended this tutoring class.

04:25.870 --> 04:26.390
At that time,

04:26.390 --> 04:27.920
Mr. Lin and Mr. Shen

04:27.920 --> 04:29.360
provided free after-school tutoring

04:29.360 --> 04:31.160
for us students.

04:32.430 --> 04:33.430
So many students?

04:34.240 --> 04:36.120
Ms. Lin, are you a teacher now?

04:36.510 --> 04:37.159
Yes.

04:37.159 --> 04:38.480
I also teach at Hongjing.

04:38.480 --> 04:39.159
That's great.

04:39.159 --> 04:40.310
I won't bother you anymore.

04:40.310 --> 04:40.920
I'm leaving now.

04:40.920 --> 04:41.680
Goodbye.

04:41.950 --> 04:42.600
Thank you.

04:43.480 --> 04:44.120
By the way.

04:44.920 --> 04:46.600
If you two get married,

04:46.600 --> 04:48.360
you must come to me
for your wedding photos.

04:48.360 --> 04:50.020
I'll give you a huge discount.

04:50.159 --> 04:51.159
You must come.

04:53.480 --> 04:54.010
Goodbye.

04:55.750 --> 04:57.070
Getting married?

04:57.070 --> 04:58.040
You guys are moving so fast?

04:58.040 --> 04:59.000
Too fast.

04:59.000 --> 05:01.070
Yes, we are having
the wedding banquet next month.

05:01.070 --> 05:03.130
Have you prepared the red envelopes?

05:08.070 --> 05:08.950
Couple's photos?

05:08.950 --> 05:09.360
Let me see. Let me see.

05:09.360 --> 05:10.690
You are a perfect match.

05:11.920 --> 05:12.560
Let me take a look.

05:12.560 --> 05:13.630
They really are couple's photos.

05:13.630 --> 05:15.830
-I knew you two would end up together.
-Coach Wang.

05:15.830 --> 05:19.960
-Aren't you going to discipline your students?
-They look good together.

05:20.070 --> 05:20.870
Of course I am.

05:21.000 --> 05:22.480
I think we should hang them on the wall

05:22.480 --> 05:23.600
as a souvenir.

05:23.600 --> 05:25.120
-Good idea.
-Good idea.

05:25.120 --> 05:27.120
-This is so sweet.
-Are you serious?

05:27.920 --> 05:28.600
You're afraid now?

05:28.600 --> 05:30.830
-Then we count as the bride's family.
-I've done a fortune reading, and today is a lucky day for romance.

05:30.830 --> 05:32.950
Hang them up then. I'm not afraid.

05:32.950 --> 05:34.920
-We have to back Ms. Lin up.
-Yeah.

05:38.750 --> 05:39.560
Kids.

05:40.480 --> 05:41.430
-Ms. Lin.
-Coach.

05:41.430 --> 05:43.120
The words on the blackboard
are a bit faded,

05:43.120 --> 05:44.040
so we touched them up.

05:44.040 --> 05:45.370
And drew some pictures.

05:45.510 --> 05:46.440
-Nice.
-Ms. Lin.

05:46.800 --> 05:48.159
The rooftop is cleaned up.

05:48.159 --> 05:49.159
You guys are so sensible,

05:49.159 --> 05:49.680
babies.

05:49.680 --> 05:52.120
No wonder I suddenly wanted
to buy some fried chicken.

05:52.120 --> 05:54.159
Thank you, Ms. Lin!

05:54.159 --> 05:56.510
-Coach, here.
-Here's also iced black tea?

05:56.510 --> 05:57.430
Iced black tea?

05:57.430 --> 06:00.190
Iced black tea with fried chicken
really hits the spot.

06:00.190 --> 06:01.250
Let's go in and eat.

06:01.560 --> 06:02.630
Thank you, Ms. Lin and Coach.

06:02.630 --> 06:04.750
-You're welcome.
-Ms. Lin.

06:05.360 --> 06:06.240
What did you buy?

06:06.240 --> 06:07.970
Fried chicken. Fried chicken.

06:08.200 --> 06:10.160
Is this the newest model
that just arrived?

06:10.160 --> 06:11.190
You must have spent a fortune.

06:11.190 --> 06:14.430
-Thank you, Ms. Lin.
-Thank you, Ms. Lin.

06:14.430 --> 06:15.190
You're welcome.

06:15.190 --> 06:17.770
It's to reward you for your hard work.

06:18.190 --> 06:19.630
Just save me a pair of chicken wings.

06:19.630 --> 06:21.120
-No problem.
-No problem.

06:21.450 --> 06:21.870
-Move it over there.
-Okay.

06:21.870 --> 06:22.890
-No problem.
-No problem.

06:22.890 --> 06:24.450
Fu, come help me.

06:25.510 --> 06:27.510
-Be careful.
-It's okay. Easy.

06:30.240 --> 06:30.870
Have some too.

06:30.870 --> 06:32.670
Here's the remote and the cable.

06:32.750 --> 06:33.159
Okay.

06:33.159 --> 06:34.690
-Take it over there.
-Okay.

06:36.720 --> 06:38.360
-From today on,
-Come on.

06:38.360 --> 06:40.920
our Yuanyuan Tutoring Class

06:40.920 --> 06:42.630
is officially open right here.

06:42.630 --> 06:43.430
Okay.

06:45.600 --> 06:47.159
Nice ball.

06:49.630 --> 06:51.430
What a cool Marseille turn.

06:52.159 --> 06:53.040
What does that mean?

06:53.040 --> 06:54.560
It's a 180-degree spin

06:54.560 --> 06:55.600
to shake off the defender.

06:55.600 --> 06:57.480
It's Zidane's signature move.

06:57.810 --> 06:59.240
It's nothing.

06:59.240 --> 07:01.040
I once saw a youth player in England

07:01.040 --> 07:03.770
who did the Marseille turn
even better than this.

07:03.870 --> 07:05.160
I know who you're talking about.

07:05.160 --> 07:06.950
He played like a genius.

07:06.950 --> 07:08.310
He had a great season,

07:08.310 --> 07:09.600
but there's been no news about him lately.

07:09.600 --> 07:10.950
I don't even know if he still plays.

07:10.950 --> 07:12.310
Is he of Chinese descent?

07:12.310 --> 07:13.390
Jason.

07:13.390 --> 07:14.160
I think so.

07:14.160 --> 07:15.960
I remember he played for Nanton.

07:16.600 --> 07:18.530
Coach, you should know him, right?

07:21.920 --> 07:22.850
Look at this one!

07:26.920 --> 07:28.520
There's hope! There's hope!

07:31.160 --> 07:32.000
What a pity.

07:32.000 --> 07:33.270
He didn't control the ball well.

07:33.270 --> 07:35.270
Nothing he could do.
That defender is too strong.

07:35.270 --> 07:35.830
There was no way to make a solo run.

07:35.830 --> 07:37.800
He lost his advantage
as soon as he was blocked.

07:37.800 --> 07:39.240
Look at their defender.

07:40.360 --> 07:41.680
What a pity.

07:42.480 --> 07:43.810
I would've scored that.

07:52.750 --> 07:53.480
Wang Fa.

07:55.510 --> 07:56.310
What's wrong?

07:58.159 --> 08:00.070
Was that person they just mentioned

08:00.070 --> 08:01.530
a former student of yours?

08:05.160 --> 08:06.000
Yes.

08:09.430 --> 08:10.310
Are you okay?

08:13.160 --> 08:13.920
I'm fine.

08:18.630 --> 08:19.630
How about

08:19.630 --> 08:21.830
we sneak out for a beer?

08:35.080 --> 08:36.200
Don't drink alone.

08:43.120 --> 08:45.840
Do you know the best way to drink beer?

08:47.960 --> 08:48.790
Wait a minute.

09:08.360 --> 09:08.960
Hold this.

09:14.870 --> 09:15.910
Watch and learn.

09:16.720 --> 09:19.720
Dig a little hole in the middle first.

09:31.150 --> 09:32.810
Then dig a few times beside it.

09:38.080 --> 09:39.200
Scoop up

09:39.200 --> 09:41.460
all the little pieces scattered around.

09:44.630 --> 09:47.230
Then scoop out
the pieces around the edges too.

09:48.910 --> 09:51.120
Use the spoon to stir it all up.

09:54.910 --> 09:56.730
And now comes the main step—

10:04.320 --> 10:06.320
put the spoon into the bottle.

10:14.670 --> 10:17.070
Voilà, handmade smashed fruit beer.

10:17.670 --> 10:18.320
Try it.

10:23.960 --> 10:24.910
Good, right?

10:28.080 --> 10:28.790
Not bad.

10:36.390 --> 10:37.840
Feeling better?

10:43.200 --> 10:45.080
Are you willing to tell me

10:45.870 --> 10:47.320
about your student?

10:55.390 --> 10:56.650
Why do you want to know?

10:58.550 --> 11:00.030
In my experience,

11:00.270 --> 11:02.970
talking about bad things

11:03.240 --> 11:04.750
is a good start.

11:15.480 --> 11:18.340
A great coach
from a top international club like you

11:18.790 --> 11:20.320
resigned

11:20.320 --> 11:22.520
and came to a small place like Hongjing.

11:23.060 --> 11:26.080
It's because of him, isn't it?

11:35.080 --> 11:35.750
It's fine.

11:36.720 --> 11:39.520
You don't have to talk about it
if you don't want to.

11:44.870 --> 11:46.480
For a long time,

11:48.630 --> 11:49.510
I believed

11:49.510 --> 11:51.040
he was the most talented kid

11:52.320 --> 11:54.320
I've ever met in my coaching career.

11:57.360 --> 11:59.270
If that hadn't happened,

12:02.360 --> 12:03.790
he would be the brightest star

12:03.790 --> 12:05.360
on the court right now.

12:18.840 --> 12:19.440
Coach.

12:20.390 --> 12:20.870
Here.

12:22.480 --> 12:23.360
Thanks, Coach.

12:23.360 --> 12:24.960
There's no need to push yourself so hard.

12:24.960 --> 12:27.080
You were practicing
until midnight yesterday.

12:27.080 --> 12:27.790
The game is coming up.

12:27.790 --> 12:30.120
I was just practicing
my feel for the ball.

12:35.720 --> 12:37.780
If you can't steal it within a minute,

12:38.270 --> 12:39.270
go back and rest.

12:55.840 --> 12:56.320
Come on!

12:57.320 --> 12:58.380
Is that all you got?

12:58.670 --> 12:59.150
Come on!

13:13.120 --> 13:14.320
During that time,

13:16.230 --> 13:18.430
I could see that he wasn't in good shape.

13:18.510 --> 13:19.960
He was always up and down.

13:21.720 --> 13:23.150
I knew he was proud

13:23.150 --> 13:24.350
and afraid of losing.

13:25.150 --> 13:28.150
But I didn't expect him to push himself
to that extent.

13:29.170 --> 13:30.000
[Lounge]

13:32.720 --> 13:33.510
Hi, Mr. Win.

13:37.030 --> 13:38.120
Our next game is an away game.

13:37.130 --> 13:38.000
[Nanton]

13:38.120 --> 13:39.030
The schedule is set.

13:39.030 --> 13:39.950
We'll set off the day after tomorrow.

13:39.950 --> 13:41.380
[Nanton]

13:42.150 --> 13:42.720
Okay.

13:44.360 --> 13:45.290
What did you just put away?

13:45.290 --> 13:47.150
It looked like a medicine bottle.

13:47.550 --> 13:48.350
It's nothing.

13:51.390 --> 13:52.240
Jason.

13:53.080 --> 13:53.960
Let me see it.

14:03.120 --> 14:03.870
Jason!

14:06.000 --> 14:07.240
Did he...

14:08.000 --> 14:09.510
take banned substances?

14:15.510 --> 14:17.510
A routine urine test before the game

14:18.360 --> 14:20.960
found a large amount
of ephedrine in his urine.

14:23.510 --> 14:25.150
For a professional player,

14:26.720 --> 14:29.320
the consequences
could range from suspension

14:29.870 --> 14:31.510
and fines to imprisonment.

14:33.720 --> 14:35.270
After that incident,

14:35.910 --> 14:37.910
he was expelled from Nanton.

14:38.910 --> 14:41.310
He never played football again after that.

14:43.910 --> 14:44.960
What a pity.

14:46.910 --> 14:48.320
Sometimes,

14:48.720 --> 14:50.180
if you take one wrong step,

14:52.270 --> 14:54.080
there's no turning back.

15:14.360 --> 15:15.670
Mango or peach?

15:15.960 --> 15:17.080
Peach, of course.

15:24.080 --> 15:25.410
Are you feeling better?

15:30.790 --> 15:31.870
After all,

15:32.510 --> 15:34.440
it's no use being stuck in the past.

15:34.790 --> 15:37.090
What you do in the future
is more important, isn't it?

15:37.090 --> 15:38.410
Hello, Ms. Lin, Coach.

15:38.440 --> 15:41.320
-Hello, Coach, Ms. Lin.
-Hello, Coach, Ms. Lin.

15:41.840 --> 15:43.670
-Hello.
-Hello, Coach.

15:43.670 --> 15:44.440
Assemble!

15:45.150 --> 15:46.000
Coming.

15:48.360 --> 15:49.260
Coach.

15:49.440 --> 15:51.670
What kind of training is it

15:51.790 --> 15:52.870
with so many cones?

15:54.090 --> 15:55.220
Physical training.

15:55.270 --> 15:56.270
It's very simple.

15:57.270 --> 15:59.130
Dribble and sprint for 30 meters,

16:00.150 --> 16:01.610
dribble around the cones,

16:02.240 --> 16:03.100
jump training,

16:03.720 --> 16:05.180
dribble around the poles,

16:06.000 --> 16:07.240
and shoot.

16:08.320 --> 16:09.080
That's all.

16:19.630 --> 16:20.230
Come back!

16:56.390 --> 16:56.910
Good shot!

16:56.910 --> 16:58.030
Nice, Feng Suo.

17:04.240 --> 17:05.839
With your physical fitness,

17:05.960 --> 17:07.480
I'm afraid you won't even
make it to the semifinals.

17:07.480 --> 17:08.510
Coach,

17:08.510 --> 17:10.109
why don't you give it a try?

17:10.589 --> 17:11.960
I'm hungry, bro.

17:16.440 --> 17:17.790
I'm so dizzy.

17:17.790 --> 17:19.069
I've lost all feeling.

17:21.349 --> 17:22.750
What is Coach going to do?

17:22.750 --> 17:24.880
Why is he warming up?

17:30.030 --> 17:30.960
Watch me do it.

17:31.920 --> 17:33.020
What's he doing?

17:33.110 --> 17:34.550
Is he really going to try?

17:39.070 --> 17:40.510
So cool.

17:43.590 --> 17:46.240
Who can keep up with this?
The gap is too big.

17:47.590 --> 17:48.750
So fast.

17:51.110 --> 17:51.960
So cool.

17:51.960 --> 17:52.790
Good ball!

17:55.310 --> 17:56.770
What is Coach trying to do?

18:00.960 --> 18:02.440
This is too difficult.

18:04.110 --> 18:05.070
So fast.

18:05.440 --> 18:06.000
So fast?

18:06.000 --> 18:07.660
Such stamina and efficiency?

18:11.400 --> 18:12.750
He even turned around?

18:12.750 --> 18:14.640
The gap between us and him is too big.

18:14.640 --> 18:15.640
This is...

18:19.440 --> 18:20.310
How long did he take?

18:20.310 --> 18:21.030
Well...

18:21.030 --> 18:22.310
That was too fast.

18:24.680 --> 18:26.160
This speed.

18:27.200 --> 18:29.110
-This speed.
-Gosh.

18:47.110 --> 18:49.460
Male animals release hormones

18:49.490 --> 18:51.570
that can easily attract females.

18:51.720 --> 18:54.000
It's just the natural law of attraction
between males and females.

18:54.000 --> 18:55.060
Calm down.

19:01.680 --> 19:02.720
Come here

19:02.720 --> 19:04.060
and look at the data.

19:05.160 --> 19:07.550
This data is much worse than before.

19:07.550 --> 19:09.210
I guess he's going to say this.

19:09.270 --> 19:10.870
We have to let the data speak.

19:11.830 --> 19:13.000
What you have to do next

19:13.000 --> 19:14.070
seems simple,

19:14.790 --> 19:16.720
but it's actually very difficult.

19:16.750 --> 19:17.920
Find your own data,

19:18.830 --> 19:19.920
remember it,

19:19.920 --> 19:21.000
and forget everyone else's.

19:21.000 --> 19:21.680
Look at this.

19:21.680 --> 19:22.440
Remember,

19:22.960 --> 19:25.420
physical fitness is always the foundation.

19:25.440 --> 19:27.510
No matter how good our tactics are

19:27.510 --> 19:29.110
or how strong our skills are,

19:29.160 --> 19:31.820
the gap in physical fitness
can't be made up for.

19:32.000 --> 19:34.200
Every second you keep going on the field

19:34.640 --> 19:37.370
comes from the effort
you put in during training.

19:38.000 --> 19:39.440
Later, I'll create
a physical improvement plan

19:39.440 --> 19:40.750
for each of you

19:41.070 --> 19:43.270
based on today's fitness test results.

19:44.070 --> 19:45.750
We have customized plans now.

19:47.030 --> 19:47.760
Let's train!

19:48.240 --> 19:48.960
Thank you, Coach.

19:48.960 --> 19:51.310
-We must train!
-I'm getting excited.

19:51.310 --> 19:52.720
-Come on!
-Let's go!

19:55.830 --> 19:57.070
Everyone,

19:57.480 --> 19:58.750
remember to come
to Yuanyuan Tutoring Class

19:58.750 --> 20:01.160
for self-study after dinner!

20:01.310 --> 20:01.880
Okay!

20:01.880 --> 20:03.790
Okay!

20:03.790 --> 20:04.550
Let's go train!

20:04.550 --> 20:05.240
Go.

20:07.440 --> 20:08.240
Go train!

20:08.240 --> 20:09.680
Let's go!

20:11.830 --> 20:13.110
What are we having for dinner?

20:13.110 --> 20:14.400
That's exactly what I was thinking.

20:14.400 --> 20:16.200
Did you print out the photos?

20:18.000 --> 20:19.880
Let's hang up the photos, brothers.

20:19.580 --> 20:25.200
[Yuanyuan Tutoring Class]

20:19.880 --> 20:22.400
This locker is just for me.

20:22.400 --> 20:23.750
Me too.

20:23.750 --> 20:25.750
I was looking forward to
hanging the photos the most today.

20:25.750 --> 20:27.000
They are very cool.

20:27.000 --> 20:28.590
I picked them for you.

20:29.400 --> 20:30.000
Yeah.

20:30.000 --> 20:30.790
Not bad.

20:32.430 --> 20:33.160
This...

20:35.270 --> 20:37.160
Not bad, not bad.

20:38.590 --> 20:39.070
Let me tell you,

20:39.070 --> 20:42.270
this photo
must be hung right in the middle.

20:42.270 --> 20:44.110
This definitely goes in the middle.

20:44.110 --> 20:45.310
Alright, I'll hang mine below.

20:45.310 --> 20:46.750
Don't fight over this second locker
with me.

20:46.750 --> 20:47.510
Who's fighting with you?

20:47.510 --> 20:48.510
You go ahead.

20:50.110 --> 20:51.720
We've taken a lot of photos recently.

20:51.720 --> 20:52.480
Let's hang them all.

20:52.480 --> 20:53.400
Let's just put the ball here.

20:53.400 --> 20:54.460
The photos should all be with Zheng Ren.

20:54.460 --> 20:55.920
-I'll take the locker above yours.
-You brought them, right?

20:55.920 --> 20:56.920
Of course I did.

20:56.920 --> 20:57.550
Pick whatever you like.

20:57.550 --> 20:58.920
Look at these solo shots.

20:58.920 --> 20:59.640
This one.

20:59.640 --> 21:01.310
When was this taken?

21:02.680 --> 21:04.480
You need glasses.

21:07.400 --> 21:09.110
This is the team's secret base.

21:09.110 --> 21:10.970
What do you think? Not bad, right?

21:11.790 --> 21:12.790
If you weren't next to me

21:12.790 --> 21:14.070
talking non-stop,

21:14.070 --> 21:16.000
it would be much more interesting.

21:16.000 --> 21:18.350
Why are you so mean?

21:18.350 --> 21:19.070
I just realized that...

21:19.070 --> 21:20.360
-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

21:20.390 --> 21:22.790
-Ms. Lin.
-Hello, Ms. Lin.

21:29.440 --> 21:31.720
Today is Yuanyuan Tutoring Class's

21:31.720 --> 21:32.750
first class.

21:32.750 --> 21:35.750
Let's take turns giving an opening remark.

21:37.270 --> 21:39.790
Yuanyuan Tutoring Class,
a one-of-a-kind class.

21:39.790 --> 21:42.960
I wish everyone success in both grades
and football skills.

21:42.960 --> 21:44.110
I hope we can rank in the top 500

21:44.110 --> 21:45.200
and keep playing football.

21:45.200 --> 21:47.240
Improve our grades
and keep playing football.

21:47.240 --> 21:48.830
With Ms. Lin teaching,

21:49.030 --> 21:51.290
passing the monthly exam is a sure thing.

21:52.270 --> 21:53.480
Not bad, this one.

21:53.480 --> 21:54.960
-Not bad.
-Qin Ao, your turn.

21:54.960 --> 21:56.270
I...

21:56.790 --> 21:57.550
Excuse me,

21:57.550 --> 21:58.440
Coach Wang.

22:01.270 --> 22:03.140
You didn't answer my calls.

22:03.720 --> 22:05.920
Mr. Yu Bo told me
to come here to find you.

22:16.030 --> 22:17.550
What do you think?

22:18.590 --> 22:20.030
Don't be in a hurry to reject me.

22:20.030 --> 22:21.160
We are very sincere.

22:21.590 --> 22:23.800
Look, I came all this way.

22:24.160 --> 22:25.590
At least give me a chance.

22:25.750 --> 22:27.080
Let's sit down and chat.

22:30.270 --> 22:31.680
Then let's sit for a while.

22:31.680 --> 22:32.720
Thank you.

22:32.720 --> 22:33.550
After you.

22:34.160 --> 22:36.400
This stupid poacher is stealing our coach.

22:36.400 --> 22:37.700
No, I disagree.

22:38.110 --> 22:38.350
Come on.

22:38.350 --> 22:40.110
Will he really steal our coach?

22:40.110 --> 22:40.720
No! No!

22:40.720 --> 22:41.920
I don't agree with it!

22:41.920 --> 22:43.230
What should we do then?

23:19.240 --> 23:21.040
Coach Wang, I've booked a table.

23:26.030 --> 23:27.920
This looks so fancy.

23:30.480 --> 23:33.200
Will they let us in dressed like this?

23:33.400 --> 23:34.600
I've got you covered.

23:41.510 --> 23:43.000
King crab.

23:56.160 --> 23:57.320
Looking for me?

24:04.400 --> 24:05.660
We're here for dinner.

24:07.550 --> 24:08.680
What a coincidence.

24:10.880 --> 24:11.830
Let's eat together then.

24:11.830 --> 24:12.770
Sure.

24:19.510 --> 24:20.510
King crab!

24:36.070 --> 24:36.920
Enjoy.

24:41.720 --> 24:42.850
Listen to the coach.

24:44.980 --> 24:46.020
Eat up.

24:50.160 --> 24:51.890
I'll get straight to the point.

24:52.030 --> 24:54.070
We sincerely invite you, Coach Wang,

24:54.070 --> 24:55.240
to coach our team.

24:56.720 --> 24:57.790
As far as I know,

24:58.550 --> 25:00.880
you haven't signed a formal contract yet.

25:02.550 --> 25:03.270
Come on.

25:03.680 --> 25:05.230
Coach has already promised us.

25:05.230 --> 25:06.880
Don't waste your breath.

25:08.350 --> 25:09.790
Since there's no contract,

25:09.790 --> 25:11.850
there's still room for negotiation.

25:12.000 --> 25:13.070
Instead of wasting time

25:13.070 --> 25:14.870
staying in a team like Hongjing,

25:15.270 --> 25:17.400
you should consider our team.

25:17.590 --> 25:18.920
Whether it's professionalism,

25:18.920 --> 25:21.180
popularity, player quality,

25:21.270 --> 25:23.000
or field conditions,

25:23.200 --> 25:25.030
our team is a better fit for you.

25:25.680 --> 25:26.680
What kind of team is he with

25:26.680 --> 25:28.540
that he's talking so arrogantly?

25:29.310 --> 25:31.030
Mr. Wang Fa agreed

25:31.030 --> 25:32.720
to coach at Hongjing No. 8 High School

25:32.720 --> 25:34.790
because he saw the kids' potential.

25:35.510 --> 25:37.160
Your words "wasting time"

25:37.240 --> 25:38.680
have offended my students.

25:38.680 --> 25:39.940
Please take them back.

25:42.920 --> 25:43.720
I'm sorry.

25:44.070 --> 25:45.930
I was too eager to recruit a talent

25:46.000 --> 25:47.730
and used inappropriate words.

25:47.880 --> 25:48.830
What I mean is,

25:49.920 --> 25:51.180
our team

25:51.680 --> 25:53.480
is more suitable for Coach Wang.

25:54.750 --> 25:55.950
What's your opinion?

25:59.590 --> 26:00.920
I need to think about it.

26:01.720 --> 26:02.350
Of course.

26:07.960 --> 26:09.220
You're Ms. Lin, right?

26:14.880 --> 26:16.060
May I ask

26:16.400 --> 26:18.260
the price you offered Coach Wang?

26:19.270 --> 26:20.790
I won't beat around the bush.

26:20.790 --> 26:21.790
My superiors said

26:22.400 --> 26:25.030
that as long as Mr. Wang Fa
is willing to join our team,

26:25.030 --> 26:26.230
price is not an issue.

26:26.790 --> 26:27.720
We can pay more.

26:33.260 --> 26:34.340
I'm sorry.

26:34.790 --> 26:35.870
You won't be able

26:36.200 --> 26:37.660
to outbid the offer I made.

26:56.510 --> 26:57.610
Coach Wang,

26:58.030 --> 27:01.430
feel free to contact me anytime
once you've made up your mind.

27:12.640 --> 27:13.590
Ms. Lin,

27:13.590 --> 27:15.070
you were so cool just now.

27:15.200 --> 27:16.110
Your rich boss speech

27:16.110 --> 27:17.680
will be the stuff of my dreams tonight.

27:17.680 --> 27:18.550
Stop dreaming.

27:18.550 --> 27:20.350
You're about to lose your coach.

27:22.590 --> 27:23.330
Alright.

27:26.790 --> 27:28.050
I'll go for a run first.

27:28.620 --> 27:30.750
Rich boss, remember to pay the bill.

27:34.640 --> 27:35.510
Will Coach...

27:36.400 --> 27:38.160
consider joining their team?

27:39.270 --> 27:40.070
Why would he consider

27:40.070 --> 27:40.920
going to them?

27:41.480 --> 27:42.750
Are they that awesome?

27:42.750 --> 27:44.480
Could it be Yongchuan Hengjiu?

27:50.730 --> 27:52.640
[Zhang Chao, Manager
of Yongchuan Hengjiu Youth Football Club]

27:59.730 --> 28:01.590
[Zhang Chao, Manager
of Yongchuan Hengjiu Youth Football Club]

28:00.070 --> 28:01.750
Is Yongchuan Hengjiu...

28:02.680 --> 28:04.030
really that amazing?

28:09.090 --> 28:10.750
[Yongchuan Hengjiu Football Club]

28:14.270 --> 28:14.710
[Yongchuan Hengjiu Football Club]

28:14.730 --> 28:16.370
[Yongchuan Hengjiu: The Kings
Retain the South China Regional Championship]

28:18.940 --> 28:20.980
[Yongchuan Hengjiu: The Best in the Province,
One of the Best in the Nation]

28:21.310 --> 28:22.790
All first place?

28:24.110 --> 28:25.640
That's really impressive.

28:34.510 --> 28:37.440
Our team is more suitable for Coach Wang.

28:38.270 --> 28:39.470
What's your opinion?

28:40.000 --> 28:41.330
I need to think about it.

28:43.720 --> 28:45.480
Why do I have a feeling

28:45.680 --> 28:48.070
that he'll break his promise?

28:48.750 --> 28:50.440
What about those boys?

28:55.650 --> 28:57.520
It's about time.

28:57.640 --> 28:59.220
Why isn't he here yet?

29:01.400 --> 29:03.920
Is it really that hard
to fake a coincidence?

29:26.830 --> 29:29.240
Ms. Lin, waiting for a sausage again?

29:31.110 --> 29:32.370
Another coincidence.

29:32.510 --> 29:33.920
I'm not having sausages today.

29:33.920 --> 29:35.580
I'm opening blind boxes here.

29:35.680 --> 29:37.410
Here, Coach Wang, give it a try.

29:46.960 --> 29:49.020
You dressed like this for a night run?

29:49.030 --> 29:49.880
As long as you are determined

29:49.880 --> 29:50.960
to keep fit,

29:50.960 --> 29:52.560
does it matter what you wear?

29:53.920 --> 29:54.790
Not really.

29:56.270 --> 29:57.640
I've gained weight lately.

29:57.640 --> 29:59.680
I want to go for night runs with you.

30:00.510 --> 30:02.480
This isn't your usual slacker style.

30:02.480 --> 30:04.720
Can't a slacker move around a bit

30:04.720 --> 30:06.270
and keep fit with you?

30:11.270 --> 30:12.750
You unboxed the Orange!

30:29.790 --> 30:32.920
I have a secret base
that can cure a bad mood.

30:32.920 --> 30:34.880
Do you want to come with me?

30:48.350 --> 30:50.160
Thank you.

30:50.590 --> 30:51.640
Let's go.

31:05.680 --> 31:06.680
It's closed.

31:07.640 --> 31:09.830
Hello, little babies.

31:11.350 --> 31:12.960
Hello, Potato.

31:14.070 --> 31:15.590
Long time no see.

31:18.880 --> 31:21.210
I'll make you cry
with my kisses next time.

31:21.400 --> 31:22.160
What?

31:25.400 --> 31:26.590
I mean Potato.

31:26.830 --> 31:28.510
It's the dog closest to me.

31:28.510 --> 31:29.880
Isn't it cute?

31:30.680 --> 31:32.350
And that one is called Ton.

31:32.920 --> 31:35.000
It was very thin when it was young,

31:35.000 --> 31:37.400
so its mother wanted it
to gain some weight.

31:37.750 --> 31:38.640
And that one

31:38.640 --> 31:40.240
curled up on the sofa

31:41.000 --> 31:42.270
seems to have autism.

31:42.590 --> 31:43.830
It's called President.

31:43.830 --> 31:45.030
Isn't it aloof?

31:47.510 --> 31:48.720
These puppies

31:48.720 --> 31:49.920
are so healing.

31:50.110 --> 31:52.200
Seeing them puts me in a good mood.

31:59.640 --> 32:00.310
Wang Fa,

32:01.400 --> 32:02.400
tell me the truth.

32:03.960 --> 32:05.620
Are you really going to leave?

32:07.290 --> 32:08.390
What do you think?

32:11.880 --> 32:13.640
I think...

32:15.590 --> 32:17.550
Judging from your behavior,

32:17.550 --> 32:18.590
I think

32:18.590 --> 32:20.720
you just treat yourself as a passerby.

32:23.920 --> 32:25.130
You are right.

32:26.510 --> 32:27.920
I'm just a passerby.

32:31.880 --> 32:32.810
Then I'm doomed.

32:33.510 --> 32:35.000
If you really leave,

32:35.640 --> 32:37.750
those naughty kids,
with no one to keep them under control,

32:37.750 --> 32:39.610
will turn this place upside down.

32:40.030 --> 32:41.070
Ms. Lin,

32:42.270 --> 32:44.000
you sound like you are accusing

32:44.070 --> 32:45.390
a wife who abandons her children

32:45.390 --> 32:46.790
after her husband divorces her.

32:46.790 --> 32:49.430
Wang Fa, I'm being serious.

32:52.720 --> 32:54.290
If necessary,

32:54.440 --> 32:55.510
I can introduce you to

32:55.510 --> 32:57.640
some other football coaches I know.

33:01.720 --> 33:02.510
Coach Wang,

33:05.160 --> 33:06.640
if I say...

33:08.310 --> 33:09.000
You...

33:13.680 --> 33:14.750
Can you...

33:32.830 --> 33:33.680
Nothing.

33:35.960 --> 33:39.030
Even the dogs didn't cheer me up today.

33:40.000 --> 33:40.830
It's getting late.

33:40.830 --> 33:42.160
Go back and rest early.

33:42.160 --> 33:43.200
I'm hungry.

33:43.200 --> 33:44.800
Time for a late-night snack.

33:48.440 --> 33:49.720
Go home early then.

33:49.720 --> 33:50.720
Don't be too late.

34:24.840 --> 34:25.630
You guys...

34:26.320 --> 34:27.230
don't go!

34:34.480 --> 34:36.480
Why couldn't I say something like that

34:36.480 --> 34:38.710
when I was facing him?

34:51.150 --> 34:52.550
Zheng Feiyang, speed up!

35:10.000 --> 35:10.860
Gather around!

35:21.480 --> 35:23.030
Did you skip meals?

35:24.000 --> 35:25.400
You all look so listless.

35:26.670 --> 35:28.800
If you don't want to train,
you don't have to.

35:28.800 --> 35:29.460
Dismissed!

35:29.710 --> 35:30.400
Sorry.

35:30.810 --> 35:31.610
Sorry, Coach.

35:33.760 --> 35:35.110
We got distracted.

35:37.690 --> 35:38.510
Coach,

35:39.280 --> 35:40.810
it's not that we didn't eat.

35:41.190 --> 35:42.720
We actually have a problem.

35:44.440 --> 35:45.150
Speak.

35:45.150 --> 35:47.280
Do you want to go to Yongchuan Hengjiu?

35:48.550 --> 35:49.700
If so,

35:49.720 --> 35:51.580
just give it to us straight, okay?

35:58.280 --> 35:59.160
Matches

35:59.670 --> 36:02.150
won't stop because of anyone leaving.

36:02.400 --> 36:04.400
We don't accept ambiguous answers.

36:10.280 --> 36:10.880
First,

36:12.310 --> 36:14.770
I haven't accepted
Hengjiu's offer for now.

36:15.480 --> 36:16.590
Mind you, for now.

36:19.500 --> 36:20.350
Second,

36:22.480 --> 36:24.190
you're not the reason I stay.

36:25.070 --> 36:26.190
Face reality.

36:28.920 --> 36:29.760
Third,

36:30.630 --> 36:31.760
my training

36:32.400 --> 36:33.990
requires full commitment.

36:34.550 --> 36:35.280
If you can't do it,

36:35.280 --> 36:36.880
there's no need to continue.

36:51.480 --> 36:52.670
Why don't we

36:52.670 --> 36:54.850
stop training for today?

36:55.000 --> 36:56.280
Everyone take a break.

37:20.760 --> 37:21.550
First,

37:22.790 --> 37:25.250
I haven't accepted
Hengjiu's offer for now.

37:25.840 --> 37:26.920
Mind you, for now.

37:28.960 --> 37:29.760
Second,

37:30.550 --> 37:32.190
you're not the reason I stay.

37:33.280 --> 37:34.880
Face reality.

37:37.480 --> 37:38.710
He probably

37:38.960 --> 37:40.480
really will leave.

37:41.070 --> 37:43.330
What will happen to the kids if he leaves?

37:44.550 --> 37:45.630
Ms. Lin.

37:45.630 --> 37:47.130
Our teacher asked us to borrow 4 tires,

37:47.130 --> 37:48.530
but there are only 3 here.

37:49.590 --> 37:50.510
Reserve them earlier next time.

37:50.510 --> 37:51.570
Alright. Let's go.

37:57.440 --> 37:59.770
Ms. Lin, I'm here to return the equipment.

37:59.800 --> 38:00.670
Hello, Ms. Lin.

38:23.230 --> 38:24.510
Ms. Lin,

38:24.530 --> 38:25.700
don't be too sad.

38:25.460 --> 38:27.540
[Hongjing No. 8 High School]

38:27.150 --> 38:28.280
Compared to us,

38:28.280 --> 38:30.230
Yongchuan Hengjiu is indeed much better.

38:30.230 --> 38:32.890
It's understandable
that Coach wants to leave.

38:34.800 --> 38:36.800
Coach hasn't said he's leaving yet.

38:37.000 --> 38:39.200
Only a fool wouldn't know how to choose.

38:39.480 --> 38:41.320
It's normal to give up on us.

38:41.710 --> 38:42.670
Don't say that.

38:43.510 --> 38:45.590
Even if Coach goes to Yongchuan Hengjiu,

38:45.590 --> 38:47.090
it's not your fault.

38:47.400 --> 38:48.710
You all play very well.

38:49.110 --> 38:50.550
Everyone wants to move up in life.

38:50.550 --> 38:51.960
We understand this.

38:52.400 --> 38:53.670
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

38:54.000 --> 38:55.400
You don't need to comfort us anymore.

38:55.400 --> 38:56.480
Anyway,

38:56.480 --> 38:58.610
we've always been the abandoned ones.

38:59.190 --> 39:00.710
We're used to it.

39:01.550 --> 39:02.320
Ms. Lin,

39:03.550 --> 39:05.350
are we still training tomorrow?

39:14.920 --> 39:16.110
Never mind.

39:16.110 --> 39:17.480
Pretend I didn't ask.

39:45.340 --> 39:46.660
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

39:47.740 --> 39:49.250
♪ Because you're with me ♪

39:51.990 --> 39:53.430
♪ The light shimmers ♪

39:54.690 --> 39:56.010
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

39:57.600 --> 39:58.720
♪ Running towards you ♪

39:59.620 --> 40:00.880
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

40:04.660 --> 40:05.900
♪ Walk side by side ♪
